  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: I asked Ibn Abbas: What will be given to one who fasts the month of Ramadan and recognizes its right? He said: Prepare - O Ibn Jubayr - so that I may tell you something that your ears have never heard and that has never come to your heart. Empty yourself for what you have asked me about, for what you wanted is the knowledge of the ancients and the later ones.",
    "ur": "He said: I asked Ibn Abbas: What will be given to one who fasts the month of Ramadan and recognizes its right? He said: Prepare - O Ibn Jubayr - so that I may tell you something that your ears have never heard and that has never come to your heart. Empty yourself for what you have asked me about, for what you wanted is the knowledge of the ancients and the later ones.",
